        <h1>Kwadabuka Poultry Farm Services</h1>

        <p>At Kwadabuka Poultry Farm, we take pride in raising healthy, high-quality chickens.
        We manage the entire growth process from day-old chicks to mature birds, 
        ensuring top-tier feeding and care. Whether you need live birds or freshly slaughtered
        meat, we serve individuals, wholesalers, and catering businesses.
        </p>

        <h1>Our Poultry Services</h1>

        <h1>1. Live Chicken Sales (Unslaughtered)</h1>

        <p>We raise our chickens on a strict, nutrient-rich diet to ensure they grow strong, healthy,
           and fleshy. If you prefer to buy live birds for farming, traditional ceremonies, or personal
           slaughtering, we have a large stock available.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Healthy, fully-grown mature chickens.</li>
            <li>Excellent weight and frame.</li>
            <li>Available for bulk wholesale or single purchases.</li>
        </ul>

        <h1>2. Freshly Slaughtered Chicken</h1>

        <p>Save time with our clean, hygienic, and ready-to-cook chicken. We humanely slaughter and 
           meticulously clean our birds at peak maturity, delivering farm-fresh meat directly to your
           kitchen.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Cleaned, plucked, and prepared under strict hygienic conditions.</li>
            <li>Packaged fresh to preserve taste and nutritional value.</li>
            <li>Ideal for households, restaurants, and catering functions.</li>
        </ul>

        <h1>3. Custom Growth & Feeding</h1>

        <p>Quality starts from day one. We specialize in the careful brooding and 
        feeding of small chicks. By monitoring their environment and nutrition closely, 
        we guarantee premium poultry that meets high market standards.
        </p>

        <h1>How to Get Your Order</h1>

        <p>We make it easy and convenient for you to get your poultry order. Choose the 
           option that suits you best:
        </p>

        <h1>🚗 Reliable Delivery</h1>

        <p>We deliver straight to your doorstep, retail shop, or event venue. We ensure our 
           live birds and fresh meat are transported safely and arrive in perfect condition.
        </p>

        <h1>📍 Farm Pickup</h1>

        <p>Prefer to collect your order yourself? You are welcome to visit Kwadabuka Poultry Farm.
           Come meet our team, verify the quality of our stock, and pick up your chickens directly.
        </p>

